Hi All, the FHIR URL for the MITRE server is http://cpcds-ri.org/cpcds-server/fhir
Please checkout https://github.com/carin-alliance/cpcds-server-ri/wiki/Connectathon-README for details on authorization. I will be in breakout room 10 and can answer questions there, here on zulip, or over email (blangley@mitre.org)
Hi, this is Peng from MaxMD, we want to continue testing and download data from your endpoint, is the previous client id and secret still working?
You can see current registered clients here: http://cpcds-ri.org/cpcds-server/debug/Clients
Very minimal web ui for registering a new client: http://cpcds-ri.org/cpcds-server/oauth/register/client
I put our redirect url there but it looks like nothing happened
